race.comment: TECHNA (1) has been in the betting at the past couple of efforts and where there's smoke there's fire. Has placed over this track and trip and a much better showing would not surprise. The well-related WEXFORD MISS (2) (full to G2 winner Waterford) saves her best form for this distance range and has placed two from three when second-up. Cannot be taken lightly. TSUKINO (8) has a win and three seconds from five attempts at this trip and strips fitter second-up from the spell. Top-three credentials. TRUCK STOP HONEY (10) has won over this journey, draws the inside alley and gets some weight off with the claim. Ticks a few boxes for a race like this. GOOD PHILLY (6) best of the rest in a race with only a handful of chances.
